Subject: [PATCH 0603/4530] drm/amdgpu/ras: use GPU PAGE_SIZE/SHIFT for
 reserving pages
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

We are reserving vram pages so they should be aligned to the
GPU page size.

